views/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019"><em>《NME》</em></a>在四星评论中写道：“接下来是一部细致入微、玫瑰色的喜剧冒险片，配以由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">Lizzo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>主演的令人惊叹的流行配乐，不知怎的，它不辜负巨大的炒作。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/margot-robbie-shoots-down-barbie-sequel-i-cant-imagine-what-would-be-next-3549230">玛格特·罗比 (Margot Robbie) 驳斥《芭比娃娃》续集：“我无法想象接下来会发生什么”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
